00412 class auto_handle
00413 {
00414     public:
00415 
00416     template <typename Parameter>
00417     auto_handle(Parameter parameter)
00418     :   t_(T::create(parameter).release())

00420

00422 
00423     T* operator->() {return t_;}
00424 
00425     private:
